datasets.name: 201c5f88
queryLines:
WITH raw_data as (
    SELECT
        endpoint_usage.workspace_id,
        endpoint_usage.served_entity_id,
        served_entities.endpoint_name,
        served_entities.entity_type,
        served_entities.entity_name,
        served_entities.external_model_config,
        served_entities.foundation_model_config,
        endpoint_usage.requester,
        date_trunc('second', endpoint_usage.request_time) as request_time,
        endpoint_usage.status_code,
        endpoint_usage.input_token_count,
        endpoint_usage.output_token_count, 
        endpoint_usage.input_token_count + endpoint_usage.output_token_count AS token_count
    FROM
        system.serving.endpoint_usage
    LEFT JOIN 
        system.serving.served_entities on endpoint_usage.served_entity_id = served_entities.served_entity_id
    WHERE
        endpoint_usage.request_time BETWEEN :date_range.min AND :date_range.max
        -- Requests accounted in data
        AND (
            -- Successful Requests
            (endpoint_usage.status_code = 200)
            -- Error Code 5XX
            OR (endpoint_usage.status_code >= 500) 
            -- Rate Limit Error
            OR (endpoint_usage.status_code = 429)
        )
        AND (
            served_entities.entity_type IN ('EXTERNAL_MODEL', 'FOUNDATION_MODEL') 
            OR 
            -- Temporary condition to account for FMAPI PPT endpoints as they are not yet in the served_entities table as of the making of this query
            -- The fix for this is in progress.
            served_entities.entity_type IS NULL 
        )
    )
SELECT
    raw_data.workspace_id,
    raw_data.served_entity_id,
    raw_data.endpoint_name,
    COALESCE(raw_data.endpoint_name, raw_data.served_entity_id) as endpoint_name_or_served_entity_id,
    raw_data.entity_type,
    raw_data.entity_name,
    raw_data.external_model_config,
    raw_data.foundation_model_config,
    raw_data.requester,
    DATE_TRUNC('minute', raw_data.request_time) as request_time_minute,
    COUNT(1) as request_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 then 1 else 0 end) as successful_request_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 then 1 else 0 end) as failed_request_count,
    SUM(raw_data.input_token_count) as input_token_count,
    SUM(raw_data.output_token_count) as output_token_count,
    SUM(raw_data.token_count) as token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.input_token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_input_token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.output_token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_output_token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.input_token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_input_token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.output_token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_output_token_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_token_count
FROM
    raw_data
GROUP BY ALL

WITH raw_data as (
    SELECT
        endpoint_usage.workspace_id,
        endpoint_usage.served_entity_id,
        served_entities.endpoint_name,
        served_entities.entity_type,
        served_entities.entity_name,
        served_entities.external_model_config,
        served_entities.foundation_model_config,
        endpoint_usage.requester,
        date_trunc('second', endpoint_usage.request_time) as request_time,
        endpoint_usage.status_code,
        endpoint_usage.input_token_count,
        endpoint_usage.output_token_count, 
        endpoint_usage.input_token_count + endpoint_usage.output_token_count AS token_count
    FROM
        system.serving.endpoint_usage
    LEFT JOIN 
        system.serving.served_entities on endpoint_usage.served_entity_id = served_entities.served_entity_id
    WHERE
        endpoint_usage.request_time BETWEEN :date_range.min AND :date_range.max
        -- Requests accounted in data
        AND (
            -- Successful Requests
            (endpoint_usage.status_code = 200)
            -- Error Code 5XX
            OR (endpoint_usage.status_code >= 500) 
            -- Rate Limit Error
            OR (endpoint_usage.status_code = 429)
        )
        AND (
            served_entities.entity_type IN ('EXTERNAL_MODEL', 'FOUNDATION_MODEL') 
            OR 
            -- Temporary condition to account for FMAPI PPT endpoints as they are not yet in the served_entities table as of the making of this query
            -- The fix for this is in progress.
            served_entities.entity_type IS NULL
        )
    )
SELECT
    *,
    SUM(request_count) OVER (PARTITION BY endpoint_name_or_served_entity_id) as request_count_partition,
    SUM(token_count) OVER (PARTITION BY endpoint_name_or_served_entity_id) as token_count_partition
FROM (
    SELECT
        raw_data.requester,
        raw_data.served_entity_id,
        raw_data.endpoint_name,
        COALESCE(raw_data.endpoint_name, raw_data.served_entity_id) as endpoint_name_or_served_entity_id,
        COUNT(1) as request_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 then 1 else 0 end) as successful_request_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 then 1 else 0 end) as failed_request_count,
        SUM(raw_data.input_token_count) as input_token_count,
        SUM(raw_data.output_token_count) as output_token_count,
        SUM(raw_data.token_count) as token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.input_token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_input_token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.output_token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_output_token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code = 200 THEN raw_data.token_count ELSE 0 end) as successful_token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.input_token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_input_token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.output_token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_output_token_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN raw_data.status_code != 200 THEN raw_data.token_count ELSE 0 end) as failed_token_count
    FROM
        raw_data
    GROUP BY ALL
)
ORDER BY token_count_partition DESC, token_count DESC

datasets.name: 81755a0f
queryLines:
WITH 
    -- NOTE: Replace the source table in this CTE to your inference table
    inference_table AS (
    SELECT
        *
    FROM
        -- NOTE: CHANGE THIS TABLE TO YOUR INFERENCE TABLE
        main.default.`databricks-claude-3-7-sonnet_payload` inference_table
    WHERE
        inference_table.request_time BETWEEN :date_range.min AND :date_range.max
    )
    ,inference_table_dates_hours AS (
    SELECT
        inference_table.request_date,
        date_trunc('hour', inference_table.request_time) as request_time_hour
    FROM
        inference_table
    GROUP BY 1,2
    )
    ,request_metrics AS (
    SELECT
        request_date,
        date_trunc('hour', request_time_minute) as request_time_hour,
        SUM(request_count) as request_count,
        SUM(successful_request_count) as successful_request_count,
        MAX(request_count) as max_request_count_minute,
        MAX(successful_request_count) as max_successful_request_count_minute
    FROM (
        SELECT
            inference_table.request_date,
            date_trunc('minute', inference_table.request_time) as request_time_minute,
            COUNT(1) as request_count,
            SUM(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as successful_request_count
        FROM
            inference_table
        GROUP BY ALL
    )
    GROUP BY ALL
    )
    ,latency_metrics AS (
    SELECT
        inference_table.request_date,
        date_trunc('hour', inference_table.request_time) as request_time_hour,
        COUNT(1) as request_count,
        SUM(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as successful_request_count,
        MEAN(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN inference_table.execution_duration_ms / 1000.0 ELSE 0 END) as avg_request_execution_duration_s,
        percentile(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN inference_table.execution_duration_ms / 1000.0 ELSE 0 END, 0.5) as median_request_execution_duration_s,
        percentile(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN inference_table.execution_duration_ms / 1000.0 ELSE 0 END, 0.75) as p75_request_execution_duration_s,
        percentile(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN inference_table.execution_duration_ms / 1000.0 ELSE 0 END, 0.95) as p95_request_execution_duration_s,
        percentile(CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN inference_table.execution_duration_ms / 1000.0 ELSE 0 END, 0.99) as p99_request_execution_duration_s
    FROM
        inference_table
    GROUP BY ALL
    )
    ,concurrency_metrics_base AS (
    SELECT
        databricks_request_id,
        inference_table.request_time AS start_ts,
        TIMESTAMPADD(
            second,
            execution_duration_ms / 1000,
            inference_table.request_time
        ) AS end_ts,
        status_code
    FROM
        inference_table
    )
    ,concurrency_metrics_delta AS (
    SELECT 
        databricks_request_id,
        start_ts AS ts, 
        1 AS delta 
    FROM concurrency_metrics_base
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 
        databricks_request_id, 
        end_ts AS ts,
        -1 AS delta 
    FROM concurrency_metrics_base
    )
    ,concurrent_request_metrics AS (
    SELECT
        date_trunc('day', ts) as request_date,
        date_trunc('hour', ts) as request_time_hour,
        MAX(coalesce(concurrent_requests, 0)) as max_concurrent_requests_hour
    FROM (
        SELECT
            1,
            ts,
            SUM(delta) OVER (
            ORDER BY ts, databricks_request_id
            ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS concurrent_requests
        FROM concurrency_metrics_delta
    )
    GROUP BY ALL
    )
    ,concurrency_metrics_delta_successful AS (
    SELECT 
        databricks_request_id,
        start_ts AS ts, 
        1 AS delta 
    FROM concurrency_metrics_base
    WHERE status_code = 200
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 
        databricks_request_id, 
        end_ts AS ts,
        -1 AS delta 
    FROM concurrency_metrics_base
    WHERE status_code = 200
    )
    ,concurrent_request_metrics_successful AS (
    SELECT
        date_trunc('day', ts) as request_date,
        date_trunc('hour', ts) as request_time_hour,
        MAX(coalesce(concurrent_requests, 0)) as max_concurrent_requests_hour_successful
    FROM (
        SELECT
            1,
            ts,
            SUM(delta) OVER (
            ORDER BY ts, databricks_request_id
            ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS concurrent_requests
        FROM concurrency_metrics_delta_successful
    )
    GROUP BY ALL
    )
SELECT
    inference_table_dates_hours.request_date,
    inference_table_dates_hours.request_time_hour,
    request_metrics.request_count,
    request_metrics.successful_request_count,
    request_metrics.max_request_count_minute,
    request_metrics.max_successful_request_count_minute,
    latency_metrics.avg_request_execution_duration_s,
    latency_metrics.median_request_execution_duration_s,
    latency_metrics.p75_request_execution_duration_s,
    latency_metrics.p95_request_execution_duration_s,
    latency_metrics.p99_request_execution_duration_s,
    concurrent_request_metrics.max_concurrent_requests_hour,
    concurrent_request_metrics_successful.max_concurrent_requests_hour_successful
FROM
    inference_table_dates_hours
LEFT JOIN request_metrics ON 
    request_metrics.request_date = inference_table_dates_hours.request_date
    AND request_metrics.request_time_hour = inference_table_dates_hours.request_time_hour
LEFT JOIN latency_metrics ON 
    latency_metrics.request_date = inference_table_dates_hours.request_date
    AND latency_metrics.request_time_hour = inference_table_dates_hours.request_time_hour
LEFT JOIN concurrent_request_metrics ON 
    concurrent_request_metrics.request_date = inference_table_dates_hours.request_date
    AND concurrent_request_metrics.request_time_hour = inference_table_dates_hours.request_time_hour
LEFT JOIN concurrent_request_metrics_successful on 
    concurrent_request_metrics_successful.request_date = inference_table_dates_hours.request_date
    AND concurrent_request_metrics_successful.request_time_hour = inference_table_dates_hours.request_time_hour

WITH 
    -- NOTE: Replace the source table in this CTE to your inference table
    inference_table AS (
    SELECT
        *
    FROM
        -- NOTE: CHANGE THIS TABLE TO YOUR INFERENCE TABLE
        main.default.`databricks-claude-3-7-sonnet_payload` inference_table
    WHERE
        inference_table.request_time BETWEEN :date_range.min AND :date_range.max
        AND status_code != 200
    )
SELECT
    inference_table.request_date,
    date_trunc('hour', inference_table.request_time) as request_time_hour,
    status_code,
    COUNT(1) as total_requests
FROM
    inference_table    
GROUP BY ALL
